 and after shock compression in multifluid cases with baroclinic vorticity
 deposition on the interface between the ring and its surroundings.
 It includes experiments on the behavior of vortex rings generated at the
 open end of a shock tube captured with high-speed Schlieren imaging, experiment
s on the propagation and interaction of a vortex ring with a planar shock
 wave, and computations of vortex-interface-shock interactions.
 
